{center}
{subhead}BOBEK Virus Found{def}
{left}
{pp}
A new link-virus has been found.  The installer of the new 'BOBEK'
linkvirus is said to be the game "oozeaga", in the archive oozeaga.lha.
This new virus will add 460 bytes to every file that is opened or
executed.  That also means that even an antivirus program (that the
virus is unknown to), will infect every file it checks for virus.
The new virus patches dos.library ExNext function to spread it self.
The new virus has been given the name "BOBEK", this is the text you
can read in the end of every infected tile.
{pp}
'VirusExecutor v2.15' will find and disable this virus.
{pp}